string.name: say
string.value: Iceman… Am I also going to be frozen like that? No way….

string.name: say
string.value: The snail has been frozen. I guess this is also the work of the Ice Knight.

string.name: say
string.value: Not again...I’m scared. Will I ever be free from this curse?
